There are five abnormal states[NL]

a unit can enter:[.][NL]

1. Sleep[NL]

(Asleep and unable to move)[.][NL]

2. Silence[NL]

(Unable to use magic or staves)[.][NL]

3. Poison[.][NL]

(Take continual damage)[.][NL]

4. Berserk[NL]

(Attack enemies and allies alike)[.][NL]

5. Petrify[NL]

(Turned to stone, cannot move)[NL]

These conditions will continue for[NL]

several turns. They can be[NL]

reversed with a Restore staff.[X]

